# REC START/STOP VOLUME
Choose the volume at the start and end of movie recording.

**Options:**
- !Volume High (high)
- !Volume Medium (medium)
- !Volume Low (low)
- !Volume Off (mute)

# MS ELECTRONIC SHUTTER VOLUME
Adjust the volume of the sounds produced by the mechanical shutter.

**Options:**
- !Volume High (high)
- !Volume Medium (medium)
- !Volume Low (low)
- !Volume Off (mute)

# MS ELECTRONIC SHUTTER SOUND
Choose the sound made by the mechanical shutter.

**Options:**
- !Sound 1 1 SOUND 1
- !Sound 2 2 SOUND 2
- !Sound 3 3 SOUND 3
